<title>Convert Items to Subitems</title>
<context ID_EDIT_MAKE_SUBITEMS />

Select the items you want to convert to <link sub_items.csdoc>subitems</link>. From the <b>Edit</b> menu, select <b>Convert to Subitems</b> or right-click on the item list in the view and select <b>Convert to Subitems</b> from the popup menu. Enter information about the item that will include these subitem(s).

To convert subitems back to items, delete the item. When asked if you wish to "Delete subitems too?" answer <b>No</b>.
